metadata.name: Wind of stars
metadata.description:
Once I knew a girl. Very imperceptibly I realized that she’s into stars. She would stare at them, wondering if someone she loves could also be watching the same star. What a beautiful idea…she had a beautiful mind…
After that day I looked at the stars and wondered if she was looking at the same, but I don’t think she was.
I never saw her again and I don’t know where she is now and forgot all that dreamy stuff about the stars. That girl is gone forever. I just started drawing stars…
